structure TopologicalSpace (X : Type u) :=
  (IsOpen : Set X → Prop)
  (isOpen_univ : IsOpen Set.univ)
  (isOpen_empty : IsOpen ∅)

  (isOpen_sUnion : ∀ (S : Set (Set X)), (∀ s ∈ S, IsOpen s) → IsOpen (⋃₀ S))
